# Styling Guidelines

## SCSS Structure

Follow the established pattern from [src/scss/](mdc:src/scss/):

### Main Entry Point

- [src/scss/main.scss](mdc:src/scss/main.scss) is the main entry point
- Import in root layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)

### Component-Specific SCSS

Organize component styles in [src/scss/components/](mdc:src/scss/components/):

```scss
// Component-specific styles
.component-name {
  // Styles here

  &__element {
    // BEM naming convention
  }

  &--modifier {
    // BEM modifier styles
  }
}
```

### Vendor Styles

- Third-party overrides in [src/scss/vendors/](mdc:src/scss/vendors/)
- Debug styles in [src/scss/vendors/\_debug.scss](mdc:src/scss/vendors/_debug.scss)

