## Tailwind CSS Integration

Configuration in [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js):

### Utility-First Approach

- Use Tailwind classes for spacing, colors, and layout
- Combine with custom SCSS for complex components
- Use CSS custom properties for dynamic values

### PostCSS Configuration

Follow [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js) for processing:

```javascript
module.exports = {
  plugins: {
    tailwindcss: {},
    autoprefixer: {},
  },
};
```

## Global Styles

Use [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) for:

- CSS reset and normalization
- Global CSS custom properties
- Base element styles
- Utility classes that extend Tailwind

