## SCSS Best Practices

### Variable Usage

```scss
// Define variables for consistency
$primary-color: #007bff;
$font-family-primary: var(--font-greo);
$breakpoint-md: 768px;

// Use variables consistently
.component {
  color: $primary-color;
  font-family: $font-family-primary;
}
```

### Mixins for Reusability

```scss
// Common mixins
@mixin flex-center {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

@mixin button-base {
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 0.25rem;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}
```

### Nesting Guidelines

- Limit nesting to 3 levels deep
- Use & for pseudo-selectors and modifiers
- Group related properties together

## CSS Custom Properties

```css
:root {
  --font-greo: 'Geogrotesque', sans-serif;
  --color-primary: #007bff;
  --spacing-base: 1rem;
}

/* Use in components */
.component {
  font-family: var(--font-greo);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  padding: var(--spacing-base);
}
```

## File Organization

```
src/
├── scss/
│   ├── main.scss           # Main entry point
│   ├── components/         # Component-specific styles
│   │   ├── _header.scss
│   │   ├── _form.scss
│   │   └── _steps.scss
│   └── vendors/           # Third-party overrides
│       └── _debug.scss
├── app/
│   └── globals.css        # Global CSS styles
```

## Performance Considerations

- Use CSS modules for component isolation when needed
- Minimize global CSS
- Leverage Tailwind's purge capabilities
- Use SCSS compression in production
